立七十周年，旅遊局今起至國慶日，一連三晚在大三巴牌坊特別呈獻以&ldquo;共慶七十華誕共享偉大榮光&rdquo;為主題的光雕表演，與居民和旅客一起歡度節慶。<br />\n<br />\n光雕表演今晚8時至10時進行，明後兩晚表演則安排在7時至10時上演，在該時段內每隔15分鐘將進行約5分鐘的光雕表演，光雕表演的故事內容分兩部分，分別是&ldquo;澳門居民同心同賀&rdquo;，以及&ldquo;歡欣吉祥！共慶七十華誕&rdquo;。今晚首場表演準時在8時開始，現場吸引大批居民和旅客駐足觀賞，場面熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=8960590_aomen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fh5.newaircloud.com%2Fnews_detail%3Fnewsid%3D8960590_aomen&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=edf4f789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=8960590_aomen</a>"},{"pid":"26be925288e8fc38cf07314f93f12539e73378ee","tid":1603333,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"为庆贺中华人民共和国成立70周年<br />\n<br />\n澳门大三巴牌坊的光雕表演<br />\n将从9月29日（今天）起一连三晚<br />\n隆重上演！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/344182845_383547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F344182845_383547&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=4c44429a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/344182845_383547</a>"},{"pid":"28ac2356b4283d6689c24f416dc490c14be3ff83","tid":1603333,"uid":228337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:28:18.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0e9e483935e72b65682a791ffbefce059ab083","tid":1603333,"uid":175314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"中共柒拾週年 （1949 - 2019）<br />\n都唔知邊撚個諗呢啲寫法出嚟<br />\n死咗嘅人事物先咁寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都啱嘅，就快完㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99c1c40b2033a13379c92dab2da4d68b3b0abe5","tid":1603333,"uid":64469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:4